lead_paragraph: Pinch-hitter Franklin Gutierrez came through with a tiebreaking RBI single in the 10th inning and Nelson Cruz added a two-run homer, leading the Seattle Mariners to a 5-2 victory over the Los Angeles Angels on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Cruz Homers in Mariners' 5-2 Win Over Angels in 10 Innings
